    <item>
      <title>迈尔斯称民主党希望举行公开大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/democrats-want-an-open-convention-myers-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Signum Global Advisors 董事长兼民主党捐助者查尔斯·迈尔斯 (Charles Myers) 谈到副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 需要做些什么来团结党派并对抗唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)。他说，该党希望看到一场公开的大会。他正在参加“彭博公开利益”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/democrats-want-an-open-convention-myers-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 13:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋与毛里求斯签署经济协定，旨在促进贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/uae-signs-economic-pact-with-mauritius-aimed-at-boosting-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国与毛里求斯签署了一项经济协议，旨在增加双边贸易，特别是在金融、物流和服务领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/uae-signs-economic-pact-with-mauritius-aimed-at-boosting-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 12:51:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳寻求限制部分供应，可可期货上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/cocoa-futures-advance-as-ghana-seeks-to-restrict-some-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳计划限制下一季的部分供应，这引发了人们对持续短缺的担忧，导致可可期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/cocoa-futures-advance-as-ghana-seeks-to-restrict-some-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师 Vicenzino 谈卡马拉·哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/global-strategy-project-s-vicenzino-on-kamal-harris-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登决定不竞选连任，这让民主党人备受鼓舞，捐款激增。在拜登的支持和多位党内资深人士的支持下，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯现在明显是赢得民主党提名的领跑者。Daybreak 的汤姆·麦肯齐与策略师马可·维森齐诺谈论了美国政治现状。（更正了标题中卡马拉·哈里斯的拼写。）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/global-strategy-project-s-vicenzino-on-kamal-harris-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国政局动荡影响，油价跌至五周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估美国总统乔·拜登决定不寻求连任将如何影响市场，油价延续了近期的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股暴跌后强势反弹，收益成为焦点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者的目光不再局限于乔·拜登结束连任竞选，而是关注科技股财报季的开始，股市在经历了 4 月份以来最糟糕的一周后出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伍德赛德将斥资 9 亿美元收购 Tellurian，进军天然气领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/woodside-to-buy-us-lng-developer-tellurian-for-900-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伍德赛德能源集团有限公司 (Woodside Energy Group Ltd.) 同意以约 9 亿美元收购陷入困境的美国液化天然气出口项目开发商 Tellurian Inc.，押注全球对该燃料的需求将快速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/woodside-to-buy-us-lng-developer-tellurian-for-900-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
